OL,3,COne-word Ofsted judgements for schools
OL,4,Cscrapped immediately
OL,6,FThe government says one-word grades
OL,7,Ffor schools will be scrapped because
OL,8,Fthey 'fail to provide a fair and
OL,9,Faccurate assessment of overall school
OL,10,Fperformance'. ITV News Correspondent
OL,11,FStacey Foster reports
OL,13,FSingle-word headline Ofsted judgements
OL,14,Ffor schools will be scrapped
OL,15,Fimmediately, the government has
OL,16,Fannounced.
OL,18,FPreviously, Ofsted awarded a one-word
OL,19,Fheadline grade to schools it inspects:
OL,20,Foutstanding, good, requires
OL,21,Fimprovement and inadequate.
