OL,3,COne-word Ofsted judgements for schools
OL,4,Cscrapped immediately
OL,6,FThe announcement follows engagement
OL,7,Fwith the teaching sector and the
OL,8,Ffamily of headteacher Ruth Perry,
OL,9,Fafter a coroner's inquest found the
OL,10,FOfsted inspection process had likely
OL,11,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,13,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,14,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,15,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,16,Fhighest rating, "outstanding", to its
OL,17,Flowest rating, "inadequate", over
OL,18,Fsafeguarding concerns.
