OL,4,Cscrapped immediately
OL,6,FMrs Perry's sister, Professor Julia
OL,7,FWaters, welcomed the move, saying the
OL,8,Ffamily were "delighted and relieved".
OL,10,FThe one-word judgement will be
OL,11,Freplaced by school report cards, set
OL,12,Fto be introduced from September 2025,
OL,13,Fwhich will "provide parents with a
OL,14,Ffull and comprehensive assessment of
OL,15,Fhow schools are performing and ensure
OL,16,Fthat inspections are more effective in
OL,17,Fdriving improvement", it added.
