OL,6,FIn the meantime, parents will see the
OL,7,Ffour grades ` outstanding, good,
OL,8,Frequires improvement and inadequate `
OL,9,Fgiven across the existing sub-
OL,10,Fcategories: quality of education;
OL,11,Fbehaviour and attitudes; personal
OL,12,Fdevelopment; leadership and
OL,13,Fmanagement, the Department for
OL,14,FEducation (DfE) said.
