OL,4,Cscrapped immediately
OL,6,FIt is understood the removal of single-
OL,7,Fheadline grades for other settings
OL,8,Finspected by Ofsted ` independent
OL,9,Fschools, early years settings,
OL,10,Fcolleges, children's social care
OL,11,Fproviders and initial teacher training
OL,12,F` will follow.
OL,14,F"Single-word headline judgments are
OL,15,Fdangerous and reductive. They are
OL,16,Funpopular with parents and teachers,
OL,17,Fand their simplistic impact has made
OL,18,Fthe daily job of improving school
OL,19,Fstandards harder for everyone except
OL,20,Fthe bureaucrats," Mrs Perry's sister,
OL,21,FProf Waters said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
