OL,4,Cscrapped immediately
OL,6,F"The shame, injustice, and high-stakes
OL,7,Fconsequences of an 'inadequate'
OL,8,Fjudgement, together with the rude and
OL,9,Fintimidating conduct of the inspection
OL,10,Fitself, were the cause of my sister's
OL,11,Fmental deterioration and suicide.
OL,13,F"Single-word judgments are just the
OL,14,Fmost visible feature of a
OL,15,Ffundamentally flawed inspection
OL,16,Fsystem. Ofsted's reign of terror has
OL,17,Fcaused untold harm to headteachers and
OL,18,Fschool staff for too long, with a
OL,19,Fnegative impact on children's
OL,20,Feducation."
