OL,6,FSingle-phrase grades "fail to provide
OL,7,Fa fair and accurate assessment of
OL,8,Foverall school performance across a
OL,9,Frange of areas and are supported by a
OL,10,Fminority of parents and teachers", the
OL,11,FDfE said.
OL,13,FAs part of the announcement, where
OL,14,Fschools are identified as struggling,
OL,15,Fthe government will prioritise getting
OL,16,Fplans in place to improve the
OL,17,Feducation and experience of children,
OL,18,Frather than relying on changing
OL,19,Fschools' management, the DfE said.
