OL,6,FFrom early 2025, the government will
OL,7,Falso introduce regional improvement
OL,8,Fteams that will work with struggling
OL,9,Fschools to address areas of weakness.
OL,11,FIn cases of the most serious concern,
OL,12,Fthe government will continue to
OL,13,Fintervene, including by issuing an
OL,14,Facademy order, which may in some cases
OL,15,Fmean transferring to new management.
OL,17,FOfsted will continue to identify these
OL,18,Fschools ` which would have been graded
OL,19,Fas inadequate.
